<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,1957,2020]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
This species was described from six females with the data: 
<collectingCountry box="[842,950,1957,1983]" name="Tanzania" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Tanzania</collectingCountry>
, Rufiji River, 
<date box="[1115,1258,1957,1983]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" value="1917-08-11">
<number box="[1115,1142,1957,1983]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" value="11.0">11</number>
.viii. 
<number box="[1194,1258,1957,1983]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" value="1917.0">1917</number>
</date>
. The following notes are based on one of these females, and the species can be distinguished from the more widespread 
<emphasis box="[1414,1435,1995,2020]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">T.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
